# Documentation Diagrams

Always use Mermaid UML syntax for diagrams and charts in markdown files. Never use ASCII art or box-drawing characters.

```markdown
<!-- BAD: ASCII art -->
┌─────────┐       ┌─────────┐
│ Service A │ ───► │ Service B │
└─────────┘       └─────────┘

<!-- GOOD: Mermaid -->
```mermaid
graph LR
    A[Service A] --> B[Service B]
```
